Toss the contents of 1 package (1 pound) of Birds Eye Broccoli, Beans, Onions & Peppers in olive oil. Place them on an oven tray and roast at 450 degrees F for 15 to 20 minutes, turning occasionally. Chop a head of romaine lettuce into chunky pieces and place in bowl. Add the roasted vegetables and balsamic vinegar to taste; toss gently together.